      "date": "2011-08-24 22:32:53.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on rhel/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/534a5e76-cea0-11e0-8d02-52540025f9af).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
