      "date": "2011-10-22 18:34:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nAs discussed with Jinshan, this patch (or a follow-on patch) should add a \"file-exec.sh\" script to lustre/tests/racer/ which tries to randomly execute files in the test set.  The \"file-exec.sh\" script should copy /bin/sleep to the test namespace, sleep 0.5s and then try to execute the file to sleep for $((RANDOM % 10)) seconds (or as appropriate).  In some cases it will succeed, and in other cases the file will have been replaced.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
