      "date": "2011-11-11 21:57:36.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nHi Andreas, I'm a little confused. Are you saying we should run racer in directories of /mnt/lustre/dir1/racer and /mnt/lustre/dir2/racer, or /mnt/lustre/racer and /mnt/lustre2/racer? For the latter case, we've already started racer on every client node, so that we may not be necessary to do that.",
